</taxonomicName>
, holotype male (18.7 × 14.8 mm) (NMNS-7028–002), Lanyu Island, Taiwan; C, D, 
<taxonomicName id="06BCE1C3FFFFBA3FFABDFA37FF52FA07" baseAuthorityName="De Man, in Weber" baseAuthorityYear="1897" class="Malacostraca" family="Sesarmidae" genus="Cristarma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="30" pageNumber="921" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="eulimene">
